        <content type="html" xml:base="/cc-website/preview/blog/2025/cybersecurity-basics/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;security-first&quot;&gt;Security First&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Security isn&#x27;t optional. Learn to protect your apps from day one.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;common-vulnerabilities&quot;&gt;Common Vulnerabilities&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;1-sql-injection&quot;&gt;1. SQL Injection&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;javascript&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212733;color:#ccc9c2;&quot; class=&quot;language-javascript &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot; data-lang=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:italic;color:#5c6773;&quot;&gt;&#x2F;&#x2F; Vulnerable
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;db&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#f29e74;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ffd580;&quot;&gt;query&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#bae67e;&quot;&gt;`SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ${&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;userId&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#bae67e;&quot;&gt;}`&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ccc9c2cc;&quot;&gt;;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:italic;color:#5c6773;&quot;&gt;&#x2F;&#x2F; Safe
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;db&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#f29e74;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ffd580;&quot;&gt;query&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#bae67e;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ccc9c2cc;&quot;&gt;, &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;[userId])&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ccc9c2cc;&quot;&gt;;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;2-xss-cross-site-scripting&quot;&gt;2. XSS (Cross-Site Scripting)&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Always sanitize user input before rendering.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;3-csrf-cross-site-request-forgery&quot;&gt;3. CSRF (Cross-Site Request Forgery)&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use CSRF tokens for state-changing operations.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;security-checklist&quot;&gt;Security Checklist&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Use HTTPS everywhere&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Hash passwords (bcrypt)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Implement rate limiting&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Validate all inputs&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Keep dependencies updated&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Use security headers&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
</content>
        
